2011-08-26T05:40:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-26/centrotec-buys-stake-in-solar-thermal-company-industrial-solar.html
  Centrotec Sustainable AG (CEV)  is
acquiring a 38 percent interest in Industrial Solar GmbH through
a capital increase to expand its range in the market for solar
process heat.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
